Most of the [[physical unit]]s are named after great [[scientist]]s. By this convention, their names are immortalised. The scientists whose names are used in [[SI]] units are listed in [[List of scientists whose names are used as SI units]]. Below is the list of the scientists whose names are used in non-SI units.
